    <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Steps to Download Duplicate Electricity Bill</h3>
    <ol class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600 mb-6 list-decimal list-inside">
      <li><strong>Find your 14-digit reference number.</strong> Look on any previous bill — top-right section, labeled "Ref. No.", above the barcode.</li>
      <li><strong>Open the DISCO bill checker.</strong> Use the URLs in the table above.</li>
      <li><strong>Enter the reference number.</strong> Type all 14 digits, no dashes or spaces.</li>
      <li><strong>Click "Check Bill".</strong> Your current month's bill loads in 2–4 seconds.</li>
      <li><strong>Click "Download PDF".</strong> The PDF is saved to your device — typically under Downloads folder.</li>
      <li><strong>Print or save the PDF.</strong> The PDF includes the barcode that banks scan for payment.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Duplicate Gas Bill Download</h2>
