    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">The process is the same as for electricity bills — enter the consumer number, click Check Bill, then Download PDF. The consumer number is printed on the top-left of gas bills (below your name and address).</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Duplicate Water Bill Download</h2>
